settings.description: Galoombas! Galoombas as far as the eye can see! where do they all come from, nobody knows!
Bullets everywhere, and they're all dangerous! either they'll turn back to try to hit you again, or just seek you down for the perfect shot!

no scenery in the main area sadly.
either way, think you can brave this giant fortress and stop Boom Boom? for this time he's got some help!
so many fire bros! well, it's not too many, but still! watch your step in this heated nighttime desert level!
Mario wakes up late because his youtube channel left him 5 years ago, you will have less than 8 seconds to run quite fast, put it to the test
Traverse Bowser's airships to find and defeat him!
